{"tid":2257373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一到長假期 啲賣旗撚/NGO又出黎呃錢","createTime":"2020-10-25T06:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T06:30:51.000Z","uid":19513,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"891e68434862eaf9d96468493462211165a5ca73","tid":2257373,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"以前搵呀婆出黎企 呢家就搵小朋友出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&quot;哥哥姐姐幫手買支旗丫&quot; 拎同情 好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅十字跪低 無國界醫生對poly視而不見 樂施會唔洗講<br />\n呢家出番黎 又真係又有一班港豬跟住填表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要捐要盛之前可唔可以睇下咩機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6372771aeed3d63ae94d60c583493ee5286cb22","tid":2257373,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:04:58.000Z","msg":"上周二（23日）紅十字會輸血服務中心在輔警總部舉辦的捐血活動，疑因有抽血員佩戴具抗爭意義的飾物，警方不滿並中止捐血。港人不滿紅會拒絕公佈實情，更在調查結束前先「跪低」向警方道歉，聲言罷捐血。紅十字會最新聲明一方面再拒絕交代事件，<span class=\"red\">另一方面呼籲市民「以無私人道的精神」支持捐血服務。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200628/7W6TZ5TZKKVSC5EYKZYZGWI5DY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200628%2F7W6TZ5TZKKVSC5EYKZYZGWI5DY%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=9f5b6901\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200628%2F7W6TZ5TZKKVSC5EYKZYZGWI5DY%2F&h=00a87ff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200628/7W6TZ5TZKKVSC5EYKZYZGWI5DY/</a>"},{"pid":"9c45076c77596727831af360c937d3d4b3ca1747","tid":2257373,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:07:01.000Z","msg":"理工大學近日的「圍城戰」儼如「港版六四」，警方暴力清場，多人因此受傷。有受傷者指校內嚴重缺乏醫療資源，更有義務醫護人員被捕，如戰俘般雙手被索帶反綁坐在地上，激起多方怒批香港已陷入人道危機。<span class=\"red\">當中無國界醫生（MSF）遭網民直斥每年收取港人數億元捐款，此時卻失蹤，呼籲大家停止定期捐款。</span>雖然MSF發出有關聲明，但一眾港人仍不收貨，甚至發起杯葛行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20191121/B2NNXFQ4CVVLNW3XOKN4BRR4FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191121%2FB2NNXFQ4CVVLNW3XOKN4BRR4FI%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=2b7f2f32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191121%2FB2NNXFQ4CVVLNW3XOKN4BRR4FI%2F&h=ad8f6aad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20191121/B2NNXFQ4CVVLNW3XOKN4BRR4FI/</a>"},{"pid":"81e0515b0ac99dda525240bc3e2db2deea96656a","tid":2257373,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"近日有網民，指部分國際慈善組織在反修例風波中未有積極表態，呼籲罷捐。在「罷捐名單」內的香港世界宣明會今（28日）在facebook上回應指，對於香港失去了安寧，為事態感到十分難過及心痛，指作為救援及發展機構，面對社會衝突，<span class=\"red\">「需持著不偏不倚這信念」，指尊重每個人的意見，「渴望各方以和平方式解決問題，聆聽對方。」</span><br />\n<br />\n01唔貼link"},{"pid":"add3e12748aef0b2dddebb5291b158c6dbce654c","tid":2257373,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"紅會抽血員唔係跟HA架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88f9834fd183ea36e856e174f1c0d334aaf8ce5","tid":2257373,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"係小妹妹既話我就會買<br />\n順便可以摸下佢"}]}